===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}

The original character is [[&#64098;]]. {{Han compound|言|曷|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=speech}}. It expresses the meaning "to accuse" or "to inform." It is also used with the meaning "to meet face-to-face." The modern Jōyō kanji is a simplified form.<ref>Digital Shinjigen 2017</ref>

